---
title: Chicken Piccata with Buttery Garlic Sauce and Roasted Veggies
description: For today's dish, you'll be making a lovely buttery emulsion for roast veggies! It's the technique behind many great sauces like hollandaise, mayonnaise and aioli so sounds fancy but is actually really easy. Chemically speaking, water and fat don't mix, so we beat the butter into tiny particles so it remains suspended in the liquid.
